    "hashtag_count": 5,
    "has_emoji": false,
    "tone": "aspirational",
    "voiceover_text": "Every great city carries within it its own signature. The things you take with you long after you leave. For Dubai, it has always been its scent. A scent that captures the city's momentum. Energetic. Dynamic. Full of possibilities. You feel it in the air. In the way people gather. In the way days begin with purpose. How you carry yourself. How a room remembers your presence. It lives in contrasts. Heritage and ambition. Tradition and reinvention. Crafted by hands that understand what presence should feel like. And it doesn't matter where your story began. Here, belonging isn't inherited. It's shared, like a fragrance. A scent you remember. This is the scent of a city.",
